jKi4zf4sdBqYCDNxGWS_gRr7vTcmnyuzueOvcIWZ9BACSHHpN4pNZ4Sm-zjoGhgNcWBGT6JASmQHP_HA4MCL_eNbQxkhUbpWy4yi9_njrArIsDO2fwaiXcrTk38UKs26MHaCisTpH16xs3c7d5llTFfmW3TE7GmrO-JArR55OkmSsosjOGuiLL1WNAhNOBnT6hG9iAdPjdcm9XG5Vr10-tWq1cLqb5GQIG50mdPqCQcbzAE6jA1aI23tBn03XlDD8Zw-zPlZYM5iLTj4-D0lmnFjffceRJWMINmpUbDcPCBB8LMtshd0yclLlNZJlf83tY_ryisimj_oZvkPxnuDaG0c3-ZMQAkaIbC5YxYbYic30IDLNbUgdRw/usPGNOF0KgMwfqO7ekJ1gB-gso64zPhX/8" target="_blank"&gt;计划中的核电项目&lt;/a&gt;的费用，并为消费者提供更高的电价。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;在亚洲，可再生能力正在上升。&lt;/strong&gt;中国看到煤炭发电厂的电力在3月下降，因为可再生能源的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/3FXVeiMyqZkWeG105oim-GiobG2_Th7DRP3AHMIBGMednkWiOC3HTOJ4B4G14s4gNmao1Cn4NylijomIt-KxgxyB3231FrLGRUcQCxtdlpa3KSO_9b77dUd4txlcsjVw-C4McTLZx61N_VID4OPUoPDcdS-DOFX0EhMhbUkyMyIPz_mmkLVldeSpnXB0Ontj23FU9X_BNJ-23PQV0oXyyYtq9PqUlYBQvzS5Djz4vGYbB51VNMLB0K7LFOR4hACyiY1IGN5HuXQDWFWMNDiuVvc5Zp9pFA9rmINCACIDP0rdSp8iVmeJ5bzoueedH-Q0_Sn7SOjOvq9eO1VIviqa1EFWQJCzGps5n4QKsDdYZHA48DQIHRneyUp7hT8/ZkMnL7OIkM_4s-7v7OuNr_uCsldlwSOo/8" target="_blank"&gt;创纪录装置&lt;/a&gt;满足了更多的需求。同时，越南政府本周&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/pT9VJlBduWNSeqKqhUIXq5ei7TK0gFUjpsqKaD0rbx3QDHFiaF_LEMa5B31-WPIeATEMILFr2-JYNbZvBi4zq2K9j4qIZUk-HWVyMAUaeBbP6IF3zYGXqbTQwyCxFS8Y3jZ_lc1XPU_oJVtV74qV8BqUGknxeFWHXF14Y4tj3zsFtTyZeKHZzIZnLhb9eYGnL6rbOcVzFRsbbQrfdd4P0NHsTMaYqPVG8w9KuxT-OjJd_IOrrrEvZv5Y5HaeUaHDtJv-tDj4gzWsfigyeDe3Dm4ZCGytUPB__JVLPMOVY-gPR6h_b43WW9KEIrdhNF5OF0RagyOVF3TgAM2_njHY5t3ePwZwy9xggh_HiqtPvXD0QW4fx9UGX4jE5pk/lMnVCpR6bYdWFPWWtvmpW53uO04NiBLc/8" target="_blank"&gt;批准了一项修订的能源政策&lt;/a&gt;，该政策要求大量增加风能和太阳能的能力，因为它试图跟上日益增长的力量，同时在2050年之前结束煤炭的使用。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;值得一听&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;发展中国家每年需要数万亿美元才能过渡到清洁能源并建立气候硫化基础设施。那么钱来的呢？对美洲发展银行总裁的气候风险特别顾问Avinash Persaud加入了零，为多边发展银行（MDBS）提供更多钱的理由，该银行（MDBS）已经向全球各地的贫困国家筹集了数亿美元，其中大部分用于气候项目。现在，随着美国削减国际气候金融和欧洲国家，他的球场比以往任何时候都更加困难。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/I6PDtyn5UBCkH6yhXFoqjOvx1a6ykXLnEtOzsaurpf6KYPl0ctZYvoFsde0C7pnOswzNHqMrnik4CM4hmT51FS-mhAmgOhNtVrBllS2psFESP6CSVH38nfCgTXOh-YA-9ze4VLgOjshvxxPS5Wre0E6vQpIUm7S4HFZZnHp08DQrknF69spT91MXNLfsCzp6wqXL3DzNq-il6Rx5kTxmpxD4ttylc-mwRLdH4yBNbBwcGR4sWQWXxZCQeBymv7s7Tlp9MkqrQB4frpfhD-WTQN_N2gqBgnTwpCJkfLs8JRoZMEmsytP4e2tuLiWpGG902ZsY_dOST7f8LBTbezXhGPGcNGwXkLrlF1ZaN8PsBkTXZku9iTJ6a3gX4PA/bagXZ9qMXViv1265LlZVf42sK8fBxJiG/8" target="_blank"&gt;收听整集&lt;/a&gt;，并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/O8pSyoFH7HJnmJaOa_n2pJ3G8llapcMo_1roBKw0XDu2KtyolIeXFSYal10ZWA96NXpiPtlpGb84o3mafkWfZz_aW14XjLILOnYVfvqc41uio7lGNLOne98S3SsYaAEJjSLQWgc9kGE7sbkwxvcpLH5DoTqAg0OI2ZQGfAq1XU49Rc1BZdIUrJRA3QggYAQZmnW-z-AIKBrzZB3zrU1xchCPs2eklfK5Ojp0eF_MQmDltNS73sdTu2WYWwWos2DHPDEthjyq7hKIN-55sR-qRWPbp7wqY-gghTeyVGucPpnlg86aUdsqVllevEb_zdVTh-qJdrHe0kRRkZ_41zDv79RUhJESkAHXOXtbIxEijYJ41OAUbHdKjdbTQRo/wWXd3SZucxxRgHbWlbgjS3WlYbHq2vC6/8"&gt;在此处&lt;/a&gt;了解有关&lt;em&gt;零的&lt;/em&gt;更多信息。在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/2km8q4G7l8aW2Gs1doENRzLVH12cM2XNW8BtHSWYv7SB0GZW4FBSnMknftOg7RnOKsHElKMNtr7z4XqtrgMIySrS2t0oDvuOr5-Kq-sUWrIZ-RWyzWDtrLNFR7qC_DZj6yXqlIw8aq9x5DgC7n7vhf1gRa6YjWE9nyThMdOoiX8ZlleBlibsHjtaxaUp--bFzoG1Ipg4OmtFab3Vi-KSFeiRnqjK6c_ucyQtumNCMBcQTMHFLUuOdjbu_79x_vjKzQPAyZxVFZgUjroBCmaIGHdtPiGRineGIwxpkJzGviTpADKAzpcOCMbqHZB6mDQATdOtU5pQc3Ec8XiRhrq_qiFymV-gHbXrCDeSxqcdO0oZK_kF_nM8k5C70K0RqilA-gvW0qgZjKQL4idGbtvWG6ld6hiuGYd7VE9bp_OmrUe8IDqi-H4ZAwzihhfqDjNicNzLub30Mi29l5zjgoV7gQ659bX9c_05730FYgF09etdNftWyXFvYH2ZyEJQH46EtPH-YmmNlAq5cs8oaHYDTsFoUe68K-Ab2iKVlOWXNE8d21CTC4g7UBpuDGAlopxPoKSJbA/3vEKbfheNYcAKe_kHnX64G3zrK5V-_rK/8"&gt;苹果&lt;/a&gt;或&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloombe