1biIHx1X/8" target="_blank"&gt;优先考虑几乎没有美国人会声称的税收减免&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;推高前购物&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;美国消费者的三月&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7WJZxfZaI5uMV55KxTjKej9Op8w5N6O7GhLExdGl1jiawlK1topmSHZcbTADgiqr5QqMvR3opG_USJZJyKjLupLaTKCYovn1My4X3fYwUec7CD6cZN37dCl9t3Kuir9D7vPwM2huXTc-56HKirMFSmsOtduHrKYeQn76RT4qAJeaoqk7wQP4CYzAKlFbx54UI7O-lCvGdcflRMtdMyrWeDFzR7Vmrpsy0b15psDXv_d7tejvgYjnxsm5i_IQCYNCs1GxXcZOOrPkHdvJQ5rNoIr1NKBGDzJRE7heBSCmLUSzeS5QUanMXDFV5Ht4RBn3S9kdNNq-tF9jQ5jF9v-zE7HdWWM4pcVhtrgjcQtLd8ozqSOvd4oytkz6LAA/JiVrMXphLQ280oNM-GGkRJpxxBsW4XHR/8" target="_blank" title="文章"&gt;购物狂潮&lt;/a&gt;将在第一季度拯救经济。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;受到高关税的威胁，这肯定会在接下来的几个月中提高价格，美国人购买了汽车，电子产品以及通常从中国进口的运动配件等物品类型。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;上个月，零售销售的涨幅证实了轶事证据表明，现在急于购买，而不是后来访问&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Fo1S0_3Kj-ef8jhNOHMQ1q-BRI6w3gbtyQst-hYSH11qNcSntVEFHfmmD1d46r-hkiOaiF6TJAXqxrxG772a3enszMgs-6L-iW3446akL0Pv-wxsnvZ87XMfPgme72Uzkr3XRNBeWSpzg-_3KwFmw2X_ujlaakG9aSs_fHEJ3xleHk71DUbZrlpEt_1pxxrBPrXWQ8H1ErV2b3vM89nLN9Ri1gzseSYj3c-GG7Sj3Ca2X-m8Bwsknmh9gV1-wcSjzpvzquOsu4IBAFjIKT4kgsPuVg4HaNgUolcdTrH98UhxRbKlVvK6tqcm86qI8yB_Af7Ds7rGYPCA8fAqfgd3hS_hKcvM_128UEmY1-FwKbnDjXtoZyDkwA-xmqQ/QUUPIUxlNm5wphJGLgMlEKuvMAmFdjTM/8" target="_blank" title="文章"&gt;汽车经销店&lt;/a&gt;的任何人都可以见证。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifGQgq3Bzp7Y/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifGQgq3Bzp7Y/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;令人惊讶的提升也是提升第一季度经济活动的估计。现在，亚特兰大美联储的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/9SrdqOOYbgISr0QGuuPM9TR4KcE65cqq8ixi_ADUXSJDjkFejr1MwLPGCLQlK9WRc9p7D80V43wWaEklwadHgZzR_vMifA821oEYJ-AeuyRA4X4745ncJ4mkflLZ_7hRg-gftP2atIN0a8aeiUfRJspzDvryHMqUSxHgAd1OjKh9mEpWQ6N3HqlSqLIRmQ1a_FwbmPaQ0kC9wJrxVpqU9sQ4DAuZ6tkwbSGTf-JiLfvzcyK5gWK_uUDVp6TNlsduO9GotWL_lLYfG1LTVHBrNAlm6lbHkwsG6MpzZ-SxcHe7cetItmicIb5QC__Wfyiqp0SY4wfm8KNIcX54uUAHQLZgCYwFiATBfSgP0uwhKpni-CvLSdldcumvsDhTWU0uMwFotTQ9zGfoeNbz37B99DPVzHgYbc9kA_Vtcp990jGACb2BPGqI55POOGwt3A/eQaefFSlEWNtdSfZgybwP_KB2ZHCvSWm/8" target="_blank" title="gdpnow"&gt;GDPNOW&lt;/a&gt;预测仅显示出0.1％的下降 - 不包括黄金贸易的影响 - 比几周前预测的较大下降更好的结果。包括&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/XyINk1ibe135I4TiO2mbk5VLWQyZ3PAUVAPJgK3xlPBfNauZ1W3l7l2pNqh9PQbHlT_uJkFVLgE5mSQVz1-njKtEy5rXPn91Bn5eLuqLdXHKXU_E5hXgfHEP-sBZDaOD-aKkl2CDorGzvRCmwvhuScv6VGX3X0gKMt_zokBOi_Lv1550iHi0d7peHY31iG3sFJ9rVQtxEGXlvujFAE4Vko3hVVwBE1KDrX8PzFeoEFDRjweNJs9o84eJrkEnsnN98X0vqKcT38h2wzmwTJ_KJDAQtd8MP8w-rzy_6oil72c0Dg_wjp5chQmx5UyHSRB3z9fdYTr8Rl1VdtKJpoBby0QUPUI5XI-GbuyZpNPOEv11eY10zlXWK2jGM02B3Uo4ltmAaPRfIM2p7c1bWZ6oh6xtw3_EwSt_qu0m04Pa5vJNeCl585sGAbHk5RRJwIM8JGA4EjiekSSX_AQozQFoBC-8IJdAMK4uzQ4pfj1ISedsVqWrD_xhOd6hczO5zNuZRuo8zcwUe3uuE1GlzSL12mx2l2dg8TQetb_JmSDC1sBTkn0JN9hwsnh7A0nB_OiCZqhTaZisnqJszfzwqJVEpg7XZiKXGrplD9DWY1fZ_bSDrcSGN7FbrusnI_-jE6U4plc-OJ9vcDcavwWfsvsxlnv7jIllPoNx9IFmhNMOHX4Dp_91qcEhAgLniuXY3AHxb08dpg/Hm9-zLf_5F7v3tM4GoI4_8eiwI-hw5wU/8" target="_blank" title="彭博经济学注释"&gt;彭博经济学&lt;/a&gt;在内的许多预报员都看到较慢但仍然积极的增长。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;目前，政府关于支出，通货膨胀和劳动力市场的数据尚无关税回转的迹象。但这可能是时间问题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;华尔街的经济学家增加了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/3brs5v6qLCevoxa6tYhUFXBcaRPO-kgpfRmE_SpXBRXbIrYfMczpz2uCmPCwVIMZd2f0Ir92cbN_2w-YtLE0lepvmg0ITHp-Qzw7F2g66lGWWlCOH0JQq05g4y0ImIvglHkiNGo-eEb6CM7pehgBvH3ZPZR35xNYBjPhNpXTBrCp8785gSC2K2DyzfIxFfiHeoef76Iyjh79UP37LP0TZaLPLM0KRmP96HZ_3okTs6gHzIMuEjY4a-L0BvVYGV1gHpfjSwhDsXvyC31vJurpTQZS0JALy2_dczr8nH-Mzchs6BtJBlFlOfEJyD5mFCCNcCh9K8MRQkiixtluCtQvzOJ_gT4wjSDx-dQ-E9uT-7V6Lssd8qmC9Csz6hQ/lIfnIhmqO-npf4yPjzizNAMIwt9KT19n/8" target="_blank" title="文章"&gt;衰退的赔率&lt;/a&gt;，消费者的情绪&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/mOHdrulmn1051LYNqQHKeu5GDscDKPNXwj5j-jZzURSWRc2Hr76RqWL08c4D0AxYyWXGcjKmaN5zYnbAVOR34vuyMLdp_OXBQOtx09pxYN_2PaqGdhoMV_8tvlhvUrUqddIPh7M1efv7cuiAoUw6o8ETLO7frCN66PnjqWyfed0RLj7FejF8CHDCZbtilQodAmWauqBauS6qVfygpIhqmRjOki0eXGULhXwW_aatsP7v06Nyi27b5OzWEaK2KWOvjolQ2Rk4Y2dIU7kFWrFcfSakYkovll00RBvMK8yXuc465ttN71ZwJfHVJPEz8v6jxn68m0Z9JzCbUUV1DX_X9Ap-CL-indFkFFqRSBHKl3VG35xT6m9ksdhf6No/gOAsom-iIUMIqFOthSUZokvvLa4uh4d4/8" target="_blank" title="文章"&gt;接近1950年代的数据较低&lt;/a&gt;，而大小公司在试图弄清楚关税将如何适用于其供应链以及他们是否会将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/S3y1YHqqEYG5LEHwySwofNpBcYqAsquPApi37ArY3s1lpPdcF3NQOE4SUkQECsT3nOngdO7zDFtAYdQvF02RtK7Obv7kmryVlol7wtqpmKX4sgrJmSB90a_aIJBgTZcZlqeHQyDaDHDgEormg-MhRBZOdViBdiuyaAkdNt-TXIr2zv_cwYKOsD6WXB8UzF_O3JLamwBkSooILCfjTzuy50zgk4bydETjwP7iMYqHL1ZnXer8oMt6E0BXC6dS6K9rRq2cSJ_z1dYrxYX_MkCox82jGcnLDmgDH4mcSDnV_DZuqTvc_CGdKOlNMhap5AoQCUrMRHVnFhHTPl9Va49z6pNqmsWvzLvOcQHwgZbkUCNBypB_njybz_ITQ5o/CgYGdYzR5HUXu-ewErS8KDxfbBtGDVh4/8" target="_blank"&gt;费用传递&lt;/a&gt;给消费者时，这将是一件障碍。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）在芝加哥经济俱乐部的一次活动上发表讲话， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7KSqQBFoATaQD7YYz78heE_Z3F631Q4V07SYnyp9NxJT6JmDkQQlK4qde8hde3jF1147w3oTaec1o52saNw2_zGOjE3enhAvUhjrPGYNg23DL_hi_IHkS6-PKZ0xgEdNj2Fy-kgqLLwx-xq2gWMAwwksBq8IQ4rqlqsDrWTrr4PoLdIK4g4XN