&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;彭博经济学最好的&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普总统说，鲍威尔作为美联储负责人的解雇&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/uzKMBo1BM3e-oUMb2Z3xFR_e5RQz5O4IdHmJcTF6fw3P7zGXUIQ5NYbNgDbB6U4zPSyNA-7qTNAncBKYy33TalRQ1_ravSCLGJlGEpCaceaS1xGNsc9MOo9JhEzqP7TlRVEfv5snOQ5ZPOz9q7OvhXC0nGUSMjy-OBuxszSG5mv8hJOUa7KRV50XUkd31fFRu9OhBJwu0b1dyOaBGxGKz7Ja44XqD0giLNtagQ-Sqk511C3G2fuCO09hyrqGbNYB8Xa1KXgWIBTEy77VjkOAtq8NxPzS9fkCYCWN0rkYT99PuyAomJrgXeV0gnUFAYT2g0auyHX58uJkT16JwKQY6RnKrWamLL15w_7sSNyLxz94xwUCBDJ1upnpyxY/WmpOFQdmJq-H_iySHj0TOJQlwPWnM6Gh/8" target="_blank"&gt;不能迅速到来&lt;/a&gt;，认为美国中央银行应该已经降低了利率。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/nbBsk1fl9hfH-MNLH5ox8gs14T8syGLL8acKJUMxvLfOPMPbewBfCbIlyEe9ns7X79ag_kdeBN4eXPs_KcLNSYfps5OBF0P-chy5XCvUSWVtPMzRBj5Fbblc9X1UEWWmZmCRe1YPhApaIll_CNx8i65yhgF3qVqe3oMrsnbFnIGIVZHLpTHuoUjrohga1CV20rnW-Ztxtnhp88iTnFz4xewzi2toxlGbwqXEHZ9dkvwtD0S1G3JR40xEi722_7SQOceH4QE24DnldCAHHTDHH4YtPHc61-HjKo_h7-GACuBF-yjFXoBTciYuvBx6iui-6GLeHDMQr9dNqxNq5PwFPu0lD2CDHcPIM8goB_teS2dvoFHlCPw7aas52vM/mhZXN5kHLN-Hz-PSUdcPDM9ZiURnCWpO/8" target="_blank"&gt;韩国&lt;/a&gt;和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Y4t7cQ2ObWYwv9Dq3UP9WngQXAs9UZAfwiE6aRXX13RwDb3XqavcJpVGeqaXHXZvFcsdjoj6AJx_7TGMDfhMVl7-aPOOw8dX3PzmHiJ3DaAZzuQzMh7JhuVeTCoL93n_Q2vhArvRgL9eoKM37MhoC_loZedXELpIydQElGDKrTrgN2HZTFItaTCukeGG7rR7fQNdsP3box3327U48wNEddRNB6DuuyKw9ACk56iglnIftQdDyzhwkLi0NGXvXzS5XQOv_AgCypg6bU_uuOk-2qdx71ut23ZleUAG9l6baRpx1hfURHq_porsFIsky8EzJFm-Lf0xd_HV4k-Nn-kOlk-6zUnZrzhWO0r417Lh3wDxzpX-a61xmvktu_g/J0V1CZM11iDYICeLsJfoz68ZEVhlcBHx/8" target="_blank"&gt;乌克兰&lt;/a&gt;的中央银行保持不变的利率，而&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/0ivRxY5Xjn_pmNCGOy35qBFXxcuDmCxN5-3NmFSnFPzWzEcVt3MeLOjzZQtH7KJ0O3ogbzi1ap3aZjS6t4IsIkEWNFx1_0bR4k4feV0KDqQh8QYkEzUt7vSffnnhh1TlO9MTmoRMJaPUNitfYUpSTpV9H_25KshH-jbl67u714A6R-4Jcdhs7xR01IzLrbjTCwLvaxKewHHzCBH9qa_eEvasZxrOmoMYIdW_qxM-TysX3OT80on39Pt9mtTzHr5awHvgxCt9_1Rvro7Ahm2jktQxBLljZFj28OOOGjCDmDpQMNH5uOns2IUB-Jz-DaAf4mdjOB6eYLXt1l4HVekDF49spoNJDYuuNFFN6aHJt-EkBKB2UYU0fdSvnlk/KuOb8--eTbkQMfqMRiXswST8glb-LDhV/8" target="_blank"&gt;土耳其&lt;/a&gt;出乎意料地远足了。今天晚些时候， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ngUoBtTDJ883LT1tk4IObpssE3AanBcwLREmuTACUlK4pG53wRC5zxGLcV-5vAYstY0p8QmJ2PmCdKg1aLOlr2umnJ78WoeyjYCesSuHXD5o1D2um8WarAPHSk2qMiwiFjFLU9pMkV9cSAngOrW3gjXKn8fhfHwdIehviichBRJFM3RU2L_mZHp7Y6FuzKTqVIuo4NGB3gPHL2hYFq7Q5GjcpGXz-ZcSmqrWzWh185rVlmE__Yis5qdp-4wVlFbTEx0aEiugehWuSEstgkJVQ6V_nwLcyxwMfNod-QsAvW_X-ScNC2fIsXUEb2MglNTMj8VnjzhMuDh_KdtT3vMQ9mCtvIrIpELNJDhf8KHGKIKt4XMkP90cjAkPeDw/ozJ4sRZLl-vQ3m3cVyxeExCr20nr5Ks4/8" target="_blank"&gt;埃及&lt;/a&gt;可能会看到自2020年以来的首次削减。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;普京正在为希望投资冲突后俄罗斯的公司制定&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/QR1HKwUtgW6Z2VvMNK8EJr_T7xUh9jiEOyACSK-lda0V2nFzGl4RzuHZFrNxYxvNxqOkEN2V-4Gj97DMLvKc2uyuXXPzOaVaHePMU__v4B6_94MzDfMP4IZNj-FzFSQfSr-wvqfc1zrAEhL1tWOessyZ9U5dv9Sbe-Aej-cEmFCBiLXLmDy3kzjrCbCf9w72VAvuedpOnn8MM5cyI4602aGFOMraxS16XTAE-IVsWI_wXbXVaL-azlr9xv_N62UKNR8lsVhN_EFY4rwjQdb9lNujKJrgvHHb6lQNzlnydGlPoXM0ldZOhr0yKwz7F979RI2YxeqWcEeqn-9Wim-0AklEFaevmmJJXqf_H-aQWNvL2wQJZQ3DX1QM-nw/RcLojHqeDWuCLvele9LAv_OWuIyc7byk/8" target="_blank"&gt;法律框架&lt;/a&gt;- &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/CAf448WpvNUByqz-Lva8Kj3hk7xTsq1H_8XKEuVkNRNjjWP1MA__sov1vpPjgxf5R2uSg1sk5OcKfPFSfD7yWfzlW_hLYgzeGEnAuLmMOfQ-3mVx0NdYrDCpTc9M2dcBMfsFT44RLbIUlpbQb7pAC4C-UcCCLj-6pT1eE5CQtMxHgQNfZXgub6nz6Lrt2E4p4QOPCVuWrwIytbnBdnDxEiUAb6-Be1ai2irICSZMzDvnYoP8HCmW8EF9dQh9rgje9RDcdh4QehtJF1jy6-ivHKxMIIbbvdXrR8FvHGHxLa-RbIfuMHIHnaN9Vz5lfiBDTuV95ThGMUOA_qq4Nix8db1aPcoFEWHsluc_k-22yhfTmaTZAQGbXxPV3Qs/KYoMVW_GTIzfarQhRN1ueRkMl0Jp-QK2/8" target="_blank"&gt;公司很警惕&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;澳大利亚的失业率在三月份被勾选，即使在特朗普的关税受到打击之前， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/KN_Sjy7qKjqMHJ-hivw6bb8V4w0KjytAzTZb8u2hduIhWLWIryviR6o7jszpey0KjLapkkkc5C7uvC9skVVc25PRggqIhPfa1J-19BCWeUOHer7dKyolvZFSZDGjndMF8GJYdPlfPlyw44TXtfeGgSZkI0RjHWliPHysGIH4Kl1g7kKTkADDW670wluC0I6RLNSv3a_ZZBjnndjhJ7jl2ibXYFBqLa_64i1AhK-CVxIpW_rNTokfMeiAt2qM9nZmh4TjwU47yLgaWvpzwX4puqS3vxDYE3v-ZnTaNbyfpRPwryUdO11GygSiEzJ59Tvo5b179FWVT_hZsQvlPCDQztj3AaQ2bmHftypti9n0rY7J-24hu7Di021Ed0Y/LGqEG7Mc63Qoe5wFaOxijUAI3NIFQjrO/8" target="_blank"&gt;劳动力市场&lt;/a&gt;也较弱。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;日本的出口在3月的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/vEfdqqNANlcndzJzhhYwK4aXTVK7HY3BKxKqi1xAgwCoy5KCYCPXDlmQdryqvB8MsC-9veW8FR3ZRYGkMeWX0U0rWZDBHpsRDCvGTjwg6eSoFYADECXXq5JXW9VcMzpj46whATZSO2l_0cUn0jAlXQpMZ5V4_3k1hiG7k9CjXXwbTIEtFVtpWUVhUbaLYtLsYrN_xOMJXIPbPJKMr6OTfwvoOzZfpjJ1oXNglFEGJvpLcploaO1TmRZ49wEuec1lgtI4qa_juISwGzRP89IuEEMss9gToOv3CNMxOvPGXOkUhuWjPOPrON2A1OYZEvaxxBQZyl7PvzwTu-2H4xVPyk7nRpak51WeBuOVnOSp5TjCO7TyiErT114MvY4/aKrTAYNHetcKQBGms34mlZNAo_oYiC1i/8" target="_blank"&gt;速度较慢&lt;/a&gt;，官员们开始与美国进行正式的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SY3I8xUZfKg5Y2ipzm1qJgLBWIwcN0gzWiklaAxcZ0B2dtQkK9Ja8wwCKoBWGwXcZdHEl8QsBZgC6_GyWsh69BGp-5WlkqH0I9cFUC-eYMNdGyvfdnceAsuIZVdIcMrtIv7GQ1OnR_OZBHkKAWMTPVR3B7mkz0PTEiBRPSpOxAU3OS5iJAon2qHaBqTl16paF4uX4VYYllDWa8iKdKQFSt7AMni3Y8sD83SSJQdaTXd-Mqa12kHwvmct1_e6Bcxh9mTL_7Xafo4e1PjwSWT0AVGBZPQBe6EswwvIUiVW426KKOXvH_hNOzvNORQRMWLn01LKOp0lKnHa9tZBx_fLFph7u64irTNFQhFgEmbQskJQ6s_VVbYJYREJwng/3j-oDj7nKFDOIjFWa8X1Y9We1norowqZ/8" target="_blank"&gt;贸易会谈&lt;/a&gt;。同时， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ZuM1EHU3bAY7ICsYqFtoH1yQJ9QCFOjo1vfA3nOvSqAs6sjhFzt3psDLluFschpc9fhPraRNKjl5WbuoZVWPBfCVG8EpkK7KSFHMRZnplouStPbvVnKisOO-LTb2etZY8nzQt3xsD-lWaYXadnVyvhuuN3tjpVoIO-Qgmynx-2kftrSFJLDHOQB05MWER2dYPqSdbeVuo9Dqsj6_dRjIFixvLt3uRsAkFM2KZIoCKqS0QtCjUOVSIFzBRJRLpOUWMzVjvUqjgowoIUFhOEipxIX1IdHXTZbJyVoiIG4k4tdeE20shxwuYzxIcC_pVo-_9eYY9wozf2E9121HHHrvqaXmFFwNdmG2SktHApST_Cyif1gWJjNutbU2wpM/6lkzmnqVrJ6ua9_8LEkucOov6JjGSWRs/8" target="_blank"&gt;棚屋可能会暂停&lt;/a&gt;加息。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;如果特朗普遵循计划对从南部非洲小山王国的进口征收50％的征税的计划，莱索托有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/O-Wsp4JS7cQS_-gVfKymLQqHMz5x1vgpz7aI2cDm82JyuSt0VwXUpMg-E-P1WhG2l4xnxyq-eNoQXFTHQ_W57pLLVvBGE259pUpMNMN5FQ0-93np_Lk8VuLathpTZQdW5QqkMvsFP00_7bmCnlZU0Ft5S5SGSVtbNREg5YCVGGFZLoSxsFNAzNMQpwafRr0iUD4ZC8q2HVcoEjT-70NbSYV1-U2e9l5oxnoHPrGGIU5fqBwR8ggcDe0vcXaBF7O7-L2G8t7p9K5uwXDtcbirGj3bMv5t-owkgudgHtqnBAsA22h9LElY7KWDiAG9UwgfnUv5Y3nEv79WLw76O6d19dnxEXusz66_JsJ3p_ZDJT6J8xOUEQE2Rh6f20s/pXNKxM4tagogY4A2HejxO8Zudm2IPdB7/8" target="_blank"&gt;流动性危机&lt;/a&gt;的风险。 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;需要知识研究&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;尽管上周在美国国库中的抛售，但10年的收益率远低于1月中旬的峰值水平，部分原因是今年对经济增长的期望下降。较低的利率将暗示联邦政府在其利息法案方面的缓解。但这不是一个很好的权衡。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;阿波罗全球管理公司（Apollo Global Management Inc.）的首席经济学家托斯滕·斯洛克（Torsten Slok）在周三向客户的一份报道中强调，经济衰退对政府预算造成的损害要比从较低的收益率中弥补了利息成本的节省。假设利率下降了2个百分点（目前为期五年的财政收益率不到4％）。 Slok说，这将节省约5000亿美元的年利息。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iv6EesEjcqzo/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iv6EesEjcqzo/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;但是历史表明，在经济衰退期间，美国预算赤字占GDP的4％左右，这对应于“以2025美元衡量的美国政府财务侵蚀另外1.3万亿美元，” Slok说 - 减少了节省利息的节省。最重要的是：“降低长期衰退&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/y6dVmAYxOUAykv4l4VKBY7iBxxwMkUtFbbxxywyYCOPoquXPVpoYxn9LCMrJGF8EZii8jL72xF61ElFeYqLJ66jitjntHsdXMSrXPz1_Co_VzKWSH4Hyz3nXZgA1X5LTVkkX7YYyslT9dsG3yJ0PUFuywkLFXi72lNYqEWYPLuYZp9PnFi5Wnqq5Ept9bOxapUPq1UkDQVVc3_aFaJhaG1aNqnCwwRrH60YAGnEnr7R9IhDNp5MeNilLDDlM9b19c8lbWM3io2tW1V4aKfcin26HOnFW7qKyyrMazaQSfZejHIXZRReWI0Iyi9gpOlL2-fFJwDKLbbzEjnL_TMP03gQ_-qz84aTv52reVRf5J2C8GDb8v0VZsT6T3l8/tEMTmcwKcja679NoMpd_RWfOCewvYo_I/8" target="_blank"&gt;并不是一个好主意&lt;/a&gt;，” Slok写道。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;来自彭博社的更多信息&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;每天享受经济学吗？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;阅读更多&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SvW4DZ4kUyTBoXXD8wnrK2STwkI5Dlqr46c4Osu1npR732-UbebLRLehcL7DW4-mEpQpIRnqf6jMu7JRc5gyjfSQ2ns0lnbS6zH8-d4q-Cd_3XL6Ah0wgkgjXlW1ocSv-GUvOZEaJqsw7HuMSLHLXKzLR4YYc6AVqu8SXjWdENXysFH9WyCvnuJNt6_NBlAZyLAvRok23rDcWdKrnWuyw-LigWyjynlEFyYXfmSJFpVygGA6bI7eTGfb3yPm3FeFoJYcG7ngPZB8l_0HFGnt0GrBiZhD8fQ9uh5x6i3S4FLnMDYhOJEzcnsLd4id69dHiz8M8j31Qm8kcGBTNL3BhdRWFUl0hV-rrtKVELh1zeGiTQ98L2N-Jhxn9SQ/bJcCa0AsX3Jvp5T9LV_W_DY2FhTZ15X8/8" title="彭博网站"&gt;经济故事&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Geor